<p>$index = new Zend_Search_Lucene('/var/www/html/private/app/lucene', true);</p>

<p>I get Zend_Search_Lucene_Exception with this message:</p>

<p>Zend_Search_Lucene_Exception caught:
fopen(/var/www/html/private/app/lucene/segments): failed to open stream: No such file or directory</p>

<p>The directory /var/www/html/private/app/lucene/ extists (after running the script).
